img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k2yHS3G.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And also I’m writing children’s books (see final images)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1jEDg0w.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We also visited Australia for the first time and it was so fun</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UQ9ncuS.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I also took some time to draw a map of the USA! Such a fun project</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ejvs2Sh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So as a parent my newer comics definitely do feature some new situations with offspring but also just…my tiredness</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WRoyePd.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But life is good</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6BasBQ8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And the kids are teaching me so much</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dUnbNix.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They are 4 and 2 at the moment. We break up a lot of tiny fights</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o6p63Tg.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And we do step on a lot of toys</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ixWeBva.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’m collecting old experiences from previous decades,like the 90s - in order to show them someday</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fkOBnaC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And of course showing them our favorite movies</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7K7yEW1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We drink a lot of coffee</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ycPYYGc.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oh and this is crucial, I figured out what kind of cookies my kids don’t like - it’s these thin ginger snaps</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kg6dnmj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But seeing the world through the eyes of our kids is so hilarious</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Jd5VKqv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And teaching them how to play games is our favorite</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BINyCo1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Like teaching them how game deception is good</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JnfJwqM.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They find filth so easily</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lkj6MuE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And make road trips hilariously long</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LOSSD04.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They love my story ideas though, and they’re so encouraging</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8rHxJ17.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But again, we are falling asleep earlier than ever</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ONbWVuY.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After the daily chaos and mess</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HslmkGv.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And normal anxieties of parenthood</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O4Ehniu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>When i hear them sing it’s the most amazing thing</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qomkwZM.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And the 4 year old plays jokes on me now</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4bsPbUq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So that’s all, just stopping by</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LUDcwEQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Thanks for reading</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/t6UpL2x.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So here’s the children’s book I finished. It comes out in September, so people are already preordering it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9qdPhrE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Here’s a sneak peek of the story</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/u8fdt0S</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[nathanwpyle2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>MAGA eats bullshit.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nb09Ok3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CHkOJxD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Rather than follow the facts, MAGA eats bullshit. Non-stop FOX/bullshit.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/nb09Ok3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[IliveINyourHEADrentFREE]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I made a free spell slot tracker for DnD</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/d35lHJg</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4s5EKkq.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You can grab the files for free from my website: www.masterfuldungeons.com</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/d35lHJg</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WeaselBandit]]